('97863','33770','5','Impressive villa with magnificent views of the sea and over the golf course in Bendinat'),
('97864','33771','5','This exclusive villa with a floor space of 600m² is located on a southwest oriented plot of 2148m² in Bendinat. From here there are only a few minutes drive to the famus Marina of Portals Nous and city of Palma de Mallorca.\r\nThe luxury villa was built 1996 in the neoclassical style. Equipped with high quality materials. The main entrance on the ground floor one enters an impressive living room with fireplace and an elegant marble staircase to the 1st floor. on this level you´ll find also a dining room, a kitchen with utility room, access to the garage, a winter garden with sea views, a bedroom suite and a guest toilet. On the 1st floor there are two guest bedrooms with dressing rooms and 2 bathrooms, a smaller office space, a large library, a master bedroom with dressing room and elegant bathroom, equipped with high-quality marble. From most rooms you have access to a spacius terrace. The villa is surrounded by a beautifull maintained mediterranean garden, and offers an elevated position a fantastic with view over the bay of Palma and the sea. In the basement there is a storage room and a utility room for the oil central heating. For further technical equipment includes a central vacuum cleaner system and central air conditioning h / c\r\n'),
